      <title>加纳将失去银行贷款，可可危机加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/cocoa-crisis-deepens-as-ghana-is-set-to-lose-access-to-bank-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳将失去一项关键融资机制，因为可可作物危机导致该国没有足够的豆类来获得资金。]]></description>
